summary: Removes the fake-looking ambient and directional lights from the interior cells.
descriptionHtml:
[b]Description[/b]
Removes the fake-looking ambient and directional lights from the interior cells.

[b]Future plans[/b]
None.
This mod is not supported anymore, since there are many more complete options out there :)

[b]Changelog[/b]
Version 1.0:
* Added RealLights-base.esp (Base file containing the new Lighting Templates.)
* Removed the fake-looking ambient and directional light settings from most of the templates
author: Timscampi
